Silver Futures Reach $31.42 an Ounce, Highest Since 1980

-- B y   P a t r i c k   M c K i e r n a n
-- 
2011-02-17T17:46:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-17/silver-futures-reach-31-42-an-ounce-on-comex-in-n-y-highest-since-1980.html
Silver futures for March delivery
rose as much as 2.6 percent to $31.42 an ounce on the Comex in  New York , the highest since March 1980.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Patrick McKiernan at 
 pmckiernan@bloomberg.net  